{"tid":195002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［切腹啦屌你老母］港鐵6時47分公佈，暫停服務車站擴大至九龍塘至觀塘","createTime":"2017-04-10T10:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T11:32:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72f146eee9aac5a6c3243ec418e54227964202c8","tid":195002,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:55:09.000Z","msg":"相關報道 不斷更新：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pkXDZG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pkXDZG&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=20a212bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pkXDZG</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵公關向《立場新聞》記者表示，港鐵觀塘綫九龍灣站附近發生電力故障，觀塘綫列車服務受阻。港鐵現時觀塘綫由觀塘站至彩虹站暫停服務，來往彩虹至黃埔站之間列車6分鐘1班；來往調景嶺至觀塘站則維持8分鐘1班。港鐵現正安排免費接駁巴士，接載受影響乘客。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵6時47分公佈，暫停服務車站擴大至九龍塘至觀塘。<br />\n<br />\n有港鐵觀塘站職員向在站內未能上車的乘客表示，因為港鐵故障，現時在站內出閘不需扣錢。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源： Joey Kwok Photography"},{"pid":"2c792a7412fa6edb43f32a6f3321ee4f99588548","tid":195002,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"今次你仲唔仆街"},{"pid":"ea4ccb4606e44483625cad9340915d8f9753d99b","tid":195002,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"唔加價邊有錢搶修呀"},{"pid":"f95bc16c26cdb00f371c6488a653ef23ea7c61d5","tid":195002,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"紅綫油蔴地都出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a92235e51b2309911313ec52e8aa88a3bf5f33","tid":195002,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b74139f04df32d1588596874c2c189cfcb9b55","tid":195002,"uid":49102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"